description: Sonic the Hedgehog's 20th Anniversary celebration kicks into high gear this fall with the all-new Sonic Super Special Magazine! Get your need-for-speed on with non-stop action and tons of heroes and villains from the Sonic the Hedgehog games and cartoons! This magazine-sized, quarterly collection takes new readers on a journey into Genesis, a bombastic birthday bash with Shadow the Hedgehog, and the incredible assault on Eggman's Empire! Sonic super-fans will also be treated with part one of the Sonic Timeline, featuring new art from fan-favorite artist Jamal Peppers, as well as tons of bonus features!

volume.name: The Collector: Sonic Super Special Magazine

description:
The Adventure continues! Sonic Super Special Magazine is packed with over 100 pages of comics, news, features, never-before-seen artwork and a foil-enhanced cover by Sonic artist extraordinaire Tracy Yardley! This quarterly collection takes new readers on a take a look back at the story that changed everything: 'Sonic Adventure'! From the discovery of the United Federation to a deadly close encounter with the monstrous Chaos, Sonic super-fans will also be treated with part two of the Sonic Time Line, featuring more brand-new art from fan-favorite artist Jamal Peppers!

This is the combination of Sonic the Hedgehog 80, 81, 82, 84 and Sonic Super Specal issue 13.

volume.name: The Collector: Sonic Super Special Magazine

person_credits.name: Bill Griffith
